arChildNodes.szComment: Abasi tells the player he successfully retrieved a scarred heart--very pleased with his success.
Abasi realises the player has successfully retrieved the Dahmu Blossoms he requested.
Abasi is elated to hear the player was successful, speaking to Nyamoyo guiding them both.
Abasi speaks to being ready to prove his worth--as a warrior--to Nyamoyo
Abasi tells the player it is time they both go to Nyamoyo's shrine for the ritual.
Recognising his tired body, Abasi speaks to Nyamoyo not needing to wait long. (Abasi senses his declining heath weighing on him).
